Every woman should embrace these empowering asanas!
🌸 Skandasana – Opens hips & strengthens legs, enhancing flexibility and pelvic health.
Do it 20 rounds 
🌸 Chakichalan Asana – Tones the abdomen, improves digestion & supports reproductive health.  Do it 20 rounds both side 
🌸 Viparita Karani – Relieves stress, reduces menstrual discomfort & boosts blood circulation. Hold for 10 to 15 mins
